remediationSample:
A function CONCAT as given below can be created as a workaround in PostgreSQL.

CREATE OR REPLACE FUNCTION "concat" (text, text) RETURNS text
LANGUAGE sql AS $$
 SELECT $1 || $2;
$$;

SELECT 'A' || 'B' ,
    CONCAT('A', 'B'),
    'A' || 'B' || 'C'
    CONCAT (CONCAT('A', 'B'),'C');
